title: Purpose and Contribution
on-arrival: progress = 17
go-to: qolp_purpose 

Facilyn: The next questions are about purpose and contribution and help you discover the meaning in what you're doing. 

@qolpc_explanation
title: What are these questions for?
max-visits: 1
go-to: qolp_purpose; qolas_aspiration if qol-purpose != 0 and qol-aspiration = 0; qolac_accomplish if qol-aspiration != 0
tags: qol_purpose, qol_aspiration, qol_accomplish

Me: What are these questions for?

Facilyn: These three questions help you find meaning and personal relevance in your purpose. The first is about your current identity and focus. The second explores your future aspirations. The third examines your long-term impact.

# Purpose - What are we about?

@qolp_purpose
title: What are we about?
go-to: qolp_organisation if part-of = "org" 

Facilyn: The first question asks: 

Facilyn: What are we about?

- #qol_purpose

