# Purpose - Organisation - Statement of Purpose

@qolp_organisation
title: Organisational statement of purpose
on-arrival: qol-purpose = st-purpose
go-to: qolas_aspiration

Facilyn: If you're working within an organisation with a statement of purpose, you already have an answer to the first question with your Statement of Purpose: 

Paper: [+ st-purpose +]

Facilyn: The other two questions help you find personal meaning in that larger purpose. 

